|---|---|---|
| No security headers | High (XSS, clickjacking, MIME sniffing) | Add `helmet` |
| No rate limiting | High (DoS, brute force) | Add `express-rate-limit` |
| No error handler | Medium (stack trace leakage) | Global error middleware |
| No 404 handler | Low (version info disclosure) | Catch-all 404 route |
| No CORS policy | Medium (cross-origin abuse) | Explicit `cors` config |
| No body size limit | Medium (DoS via large payload) | `json({ limit: '10kb' })` |
| Hardcoded port | Low (inflexibility, info exposure) | Use `process.env.PORT` |

