| Area | Issue | Fix |
|---|---|---|
| **Security headers** | None set | Added `helmet` |
| **Rate limiting** | No protection against abuse | Added `express-rate-limit` |
| **Payload size** | No body size limit | `express.json({ limit: '10kb' })` |
| **Error handling** | No centralized handler | Added 4-arg error middleware |
| **Stack trace leaking** | Would expose internals | Suppressed in production via `NODE_ENV` |
| **404 handling** | Falls through silently | Added explicit 404 middleware |
| **Port hardcoding** | Not configurable | Uses `process.env.PORT` with fallback |
| **Graceful shutdown** | Process killed abruptly | `SIGTERM` handler closes server cleanly |

